{"tid":1688301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭解放軍件衫係違法","createTime":"2019-11-02T11:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T02:30:32.000Z","uid":189146,"like":837,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"163b1ad98fc6d99f2a43f3fb325e7cd89579f3f4","tid":1688301,"uid":189146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"嗰兩個on9仔只係讀緊中學嘅留學生 點睇都唔似係解放軍<br />\n佢件衫點嚟就唔知 但淘寶買嘅話一定犯法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dQs8af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dQs8af.png&h=4a775091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 我自己識有一個中國人研究過佢地件衫<br />\n「這種軍裝帶有臂章的，購買是絕對違法的，現在當兵的只要你復原穿過的舊軍裝必須上繳，何況是新的禮賓服還帶走臂章，背後一定有共匪支持，這裡的解放軍戰友 協會有很大的嫌疑」<br />\n「按照法律要求衣服是買不到的，那他們有，那證明他們就是在新西蘭的解放軍，假如你說不是那請他證明&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「胸前的級別資歷章都有？ 問題大了&hellip;&hellip; 一個是上蔚軍銜一個是三級士官」<br />\n<br />\n依家已經有本地media叫中國領事館個邊回應，就睇下佢地點拆呢單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49285b236791b992b6dc55581e4da356fa79bfa","tid":1688301,"uid":289751,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"陳秋實嗰幅圖邊到搵?"},{"pid":"bfa0648bb2335bc83018916e1ac0a966258f3c30","tid":1688301,"uid":189146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f49285b236791b992b6dc55581e4da356fa79bfa","tid":1688301,"uid":289751,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"陳秋實嗰幅圖邊到搵?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"佢係twitter po條片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenqiushi404/status/1190526670484070400?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenqiushi404%2Fstatus%2F1190526670484070400%3Fs%3D21&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c1b56100\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenqiushi404%2Fstatus%2F11905266